event.title: New Delhi Indian BigRock.com Users Meetup
event.description:
We are conducting a meetup for all the webmasters who use BigRock, i.e, they have bough either a domain name or web hosting with BigRock.
The meetup is to be conducted on 13th April, 2015. There is no entry charge and there is no limit on total number of entrants. The meetup is being organized by BestBigRockCoupons, a webmaster residing in New Delhi.
If you are interested, please contact us. There will be various sessions for SEO, Web Hosting and Domain Name Management and many other things.
